<hgroup><h1>Ontology-driven weak supervision for clinical entity classification in electronic health records</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Fries%20JA"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Jason A Fries</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Jason A Fries</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Center for Biomedical Informatics Research, Stanford University</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Fries%20JA"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Jason A Fries</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Steinberg%20E"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Ethan Steinberg</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3><span class="name western">Ethan Steinberg</span></h3>
<div class="p">
